9","tid":1448433,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:35:04.000Z","msg":"ocamp可以搞<br />\n但請各位fm用你既良心諗下去唔去/走唔走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\nTG群組，不停轉發出去，勢要討回雙眼，嬲到火屎呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群好多人入緊：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=06aa7a13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n睇消息去實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=dd91975e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"f32c76bd3d13a0cc8c125e41093a708f5fcffbe8","tid":1448433,"uid":210825,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"7bd8a156f24518644450963f322f3f5aaf3e330e","tid":1448433,"uid":304834,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"02c248f5e7f774af6c025b8e89695994c700d005","tid":1448433,"uid":210825,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ac134c13c620a8d62b7b154c3619ddc55212b305","tid":1448433,"uid":304834,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:37.000Z","msg":"小妹都報咗<br />\n但係依家玩咩都無心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:45.000Z","msg":"認真 呢種低沉心情唔好一直屈住<br />\n絕望感太重唔係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:29:00.000Z","msg":"目清可能講得啱&hellip;<br />\n我覺得自己去OCamp好似做錯事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:35:33.000Z","msg":"你覺得點樣可以令你開心返啲就係啱既事<br />\n情緒勒索就係想你覺得內疚 有罪疚感<br />\n日日追住啲咁depressing既新聞又發夢真係好易有情緒問題<br />\n如果覺得自己有需要 暫時俾自己休息下唔係罪<br />\n去唔去ocamp都係自己既選擇 總之就適度放鬆啦<br />\n有需要一定要搵人幫<br />\n一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05dcd3e9ed2df3a3969a11b4ac2878de2d2c84b","tid":1448433,"uid":48132,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:19:35.000Z","msg":"ocamp咁好玩點可以唔玩"},{"pid":"da106416fa9048a213369c721f52c1f62f3cef81","tid":1448433,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca28ec9311ae8fde2ae1f5e89241df862c24d293","tid":1448433,"uid":61876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:22:45.000Z","msg":"唔好話O camp 中學生更加應該要罷課添啊<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/SSStrike2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FSSStrike2019&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=e4012fc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/SSStrike2019</a> 入呢個Channel入面收集緊罷課意見"},{"pid":"5d0bd40e7c065d33aa3613a5ea1d8234e629e85b","tid":1448433,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:25:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2936a5a75e1296c8f203b6628dae0ef20050558f","tid":1448433,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:33:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73e9bc1491e1b88bc1ec7d4c1a9e65a310d22105","tid":1448433,"uid":137547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:34:50.000Z","msg":"無限期暫緩Ocamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635017eafeebc6a7ff0b55066171e889015ee3b3","tid":1448433,"uid":149435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:44:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ec2fc46be58c8b8b3d893d86882c3a6dd51561f","tid":1448433,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:45:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1e7fec7e5e0787e48b4c570c770bdd441c317c2","tid":1448433,"uid":9394,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1644d7951fa9480e56ed0ffebf31e65a572af3bb","tid":1448433,"uid":210825,"like":70,"dislike":14,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:58:21.000Z","msg":"講咗好多次抗爭同ocamp係可以並存<br />\n抗爭係持久戰黎<br />\n橡筋扯太耐都會斷啦<br />\nocamp當係俾班學生舒緩下心情又好 識下戰友都好<br />\n上完街返屋企你都會做下娛樂野睇下戲打下機聽下歌啦<br />\n點解係都要針住班學生 咁係咪所有打工仔都要放下一切娛樂先?<br />\n撞示威日子可以隨時出camp參與<br />\n咪再情緒勒索一班同路人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:46:56.000Z","msg":"至少我自己身邊既戰友全部都係ocamp識<br />\n無佢地我都未必敢單拖出黎"},{"pid":"0d1ef297bf2af16e6d3fb4255bd5acd3c0c86637","tid":1448433,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4396c599f31c69629ecf310813cf95d35b505d","tid":1448433,"uid":57738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:03:40.000Z","msg":"到咗今日咁 仲點會有心情去"},{"pid":"ea5c5fb7ba909764c8241db2a0334fbe01e5fa44","tid":1448433,"uid":72748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:07:40.000Z","msg":"就算要搞，都唔可以純玩"},{"pid":"07f16d8f07e2b7d35650c8f9b161837961f321e0","tid":1448433,"uid":18786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:09:51.000Z","msg":"仲未瞓到 同左組爸講聽日去唔到 可能後join<br />\n希望入到去唔會被人排<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefef029fa8eaebdb703f0386f2fb552f796c8d0","tid":1448433,"uid":89730,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:26:51.000Z","msg":"其實轉個形式咪仲好。<br />\n<br />\n人地ocamp 一生人一次，亦都係比個機會佢地去認識同屆同學同埋班師兄師姐，甚至係認識大學環境。咁唔應該令佢地失去左呢個機會。<br />\n<br />\n如果你話班fm無心機玩，咁咪ocamp 形式上改變囉。<br />\n一齊睇地厚天高，之後比佢地講下呢幾個月點，比佢地抒發返個感情又得<br />\n成班大學生可能個日一齊去商量有無學界活動又得<br />\n<br />\n大學ocamp咁難得聚集到咁多學生，我覺得可以善用下個優勢，唔洗一刀切話唔洗搞既"},{"pid":"9d817655f2a93fc2046f79b667808b15ac0329b5","tid":1448433,"uid":24007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:27:28.000Z","msg":"推到有人取消"},{"pid":"fd306c5ea29497682aa5a44661c51ebcca31dd15","tid":1448433,"uid":223162,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:00:38.000Z","msg":"罷搞OCamp真係好悲哀<br />\n大學生抗爭方式 = 唔玩on9野"},{"pid":"7b6d1b37929d123a9ea619c9d3ffe02b43392ff2","tid":1448433,"uid":151691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:03:49.000Z","msg":"批鬥不利運動"},{"pid":"89225fd6c3397538c7334ad83d3ccf980f82579f","tid":1448433,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:03:57.000Z","msg":"屌 罷乜撚ocamp 講緊無限罷課嘞<br />\n<br />\n成日都話未係時機？時機就係一觸即發！已經有好充分理由無限罷工！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"68d720bedbb3e6ef01b34ea37af2709da0b76a5c","tid":1448433,"uid":122954,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:12:48.000Z","msg":"支持罷搞ocamp<br />\n唔洗講乜轉變形式 班搞手淨係想玩玩玩 理撚得依家香港"},{"pid":"caa169a35d38b38cd9dacb1c40eb556f5286d4d0","tid":1448433,"uid":167878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:13:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民抗爭 背水一戰</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對港鐵不合作運動全民跳閘</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.勇武轉入地下打狗<br />\n<br />\n2.和理非要癱瘓機場<br />\n記住係針對貨運嚟搞!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宣佈成立國民自衛隊對抗警察</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為受傷被捕兄弟討回公道</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前線太多手足比捉 一定要升級癱瘓機場 全民打狗 選擇一個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1445481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1445481</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bbef8d2edd9130634864e57ab2a590be15d4e9f7","tid":1448433,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:15:15.000Z","msg":"玩得ocamp都係唔理政治 /親共<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁高期待<br />\n<br />\n有少少情緒都退出左啦<br />\n<br />\n仲玩果d只係讀書好d將來做高官既材料"},{"pid":"b85af99d5b85d024fce228781217ca10f0c5bdfd","tid":1448433,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b4396c599f31c69629ecf310813cf95d35b505d","tid":1448433,"uid":57738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:03:40.000Z","msg":"到咗今日咁 仲點會有心情去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:16:09.000Z","msg":"林鄭 盧偉聰都係hku <br />\n<br />\n總有班警察<br />\n<br />\n仔女/將來目標做政府官玩"},{"pid":"ec631813c7d52777adaf78d0c1fc341b1efd039c","tid":1448433,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:17:19.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"c315a04c5ebca85f0845a15ce2cb438dbdb0a727","tid":1448433,"uid":206210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbef8d2edd9130634864e57ab2a590be15d4e9f7","tid":1448433,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:15:15.000Z","msg":"玩得ocamp都係唔理政治 /親共<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁高期待<br />\n<br />\n有少少情緒都退出左啦<br />\n<br />\n仲玩果d只係讀書好d將來做高官既材料"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:31:51.000Z","msg":"點會係咁<br />\n唔好非黑即白<br />\n唔通唔出黎前線又叫唔理政治<br />\n文宣呢？和理非呢？<br />\n只要係同一個方向努力 都叫手足<br />\n你唔做<br />\n唔代表其他人唔做得"},{"pid":"8fb8fe5b9dfff4e30822a7fc011a7f7ce54306d2","tid":1448433,"uid":122954,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1644d7951fa9480e56ed0ffebf31e65a572af3bb","tid":1448433,"uid":210825,"like":70,"dislike":14,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:58:21.000Z","msg":"講咗好多次抗爭同ocamp係可以並存<br />\n抗爭係持久戰黎<br />\n橡筋扯太耐都會斷啦<br />\nocamp當係俾班學生舒緩下心情又好 識下戰友都好<br />\n上完街返屋企你都會做下娛樂野睇下戲打下機聽下歌啦<br />\n點解係都要針住班學生 咁係咪所有打工仔都要放下一切娛樂先?<br />\n撞示威日子可以隨時出camp參與<br />\n咪再情緒勒索一班同路人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:45:29.000Z","msg":"從來唔覺得可以並存 抗爭就一定有所犧牲 唔係得閒就出黎遊行叫下咁撚樣 唔同角色崗位犧牲既野就唔同"},{"pid":"2c01852526ce24155f0101db3c8c8ca36a4319bb","tid":1448433,"uid":84013,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:10:02.000Z","msg":"ocamp先至係文宣加吸新血好機會<br />\n唔單止要搞，重要落力搞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抗爭骨幹成員中，大學生佔一大部分<br />\n而ocamp就係新生中互相認識，成為朋友的重要一環<br />\n<br />\n簡單咁講，有一大部分人唔去ocamp既話，4年就咁摺埋讀書。希望各位搞手好好善用ocamp,擴闊圈子，加入新血。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申中學無去過遊行,大學後因大學同學鼓勵後開始初次上街"},{"pid":"c155ccc9e2e3a75b89c506ad332292b68d502dce","tid":1448433,"uid":77319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:11:08.000Z","msg":"目空ching係咪係city玩住ocamp開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d04cb84e60652facf2e2a10f5f7cf1f67b4d87","tid":1448433,"uid":150807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:11:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"41b7ffa2496ce7650addb6678cfca8d50d757dea","tid":1448433,"uid":50437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8227b256e7784395801a5c17bac43ea519ad2442","tid":1448433,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:13:59.000Z","msg":"推"}]}